data.description: Welcome to the sale of our stunning 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom home, which is only one year old. Situated in a peaceful neighborhood, this property offers the perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of the surroundings, enhanced by the presence of a beautiful lake nearby. Proceed inside this modern masterpiece and be greeted by spacious and beautifully designed bedrooms. Each room is flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The thoughtful layout and ample closet space ensure that every member of the household can enjoy their own private sanctuary. The tasteful finishes and attention to detail elevate the overall aesthetic, providing a sense of luxury and sophistication. The three full bathrooms in this home offer both convenience and indulgence. Impeccably designed with modern fixtures and fittings, these bathrooms are a haven for relaxation. Pamper yourself with a soak in the bathtub or indulge in a rejuvenating shower. The sleek design and pristine condition of these bathrooms add a touch of elegance to the overall appeal of the property. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this remarkable home with its peaceful surroundings, luxurious bedrooms, and indulgent bathrooms.
